data.description: This adorable 2 bedroom home located in the Reynolds School District is move in ready! The home offers a new kitchen with all new appliances and a new bathroom.  Both with new flooring. The enclosed back porch allows you to view the back yard which offers a new above ground pool! The detached garage has concrete floor, Electric Winch in the ceiling, offering approx. 834 square feet of storage! There is a 21x10 covered patio attached to the garage.
